casebody.data:
Dustin Lee MACLEOD, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
David J. GILBERT, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158518
COA: 343583 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 31, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
